1. cs.CV (Computer Vision) - The paper deals with pose graph optimization problems that arise in SFM and SLAM, which are common computer vision applications. 
2. cs.RO (Robotics) - Pose graph optimization is also a common problem in robotics, especially in the context of SLAM. 
3. cs.LG (Machine Learning) - The paper uses Bayesian methods and Markov Chain Monte Carlo (MCMC) sampling, which are common in machine learning. 
4. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) - The paper deals with optimization and uncertainty estimation, which are common topics in AI. 
5. cs.SY (Systems and Control) - The paper deals with optimization and uncertainty estimation in the context of a system (pose graph), which could fall under the purview of systems and control.
